      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the grill to high</p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Peel and finely dice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Drain and rinse your <strong>butter beans</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>basil</strong> finely, including the stalks</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1695656360342-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1695656360342-x400.jpg",
