            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain your <strong>mozzarella</strong>, then pat and squeeze as much liquid out as you can with kitchen paper</p><p>Tear the<strong> drained mozzarella</strong> into rough, bite-sized pieces</p><p>Grate your <strong>Italian hard cheese</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1695656379666-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
