          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1695656379666-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice your<strong> ciabatta[s]</strong> in half and place in the <strong>toaster</strong> for 1-2 min or until lightly toasted</p><p>Once toasted, transfer the <strong>ciabatta halves</strong> to one side of a <strong>tin foil</strong>-lined baking tray</p><p>Add your <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> to the other side of the tray and drizzle with <strong>half </strong>your <strong>balsamic vinegar </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and a grind of<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 3 or more? Use 2 trays!</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1695656384284-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1695656384284-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1695656384284-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
