            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1695656384284-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1695656384284-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Top the <strong>toasted ciabatta halves </strong>with the <strong>beans</strong>, <strong>torn mozzarella</strong>, <strong>grated Italian hard cheese </strong>and a generous grind of<strong> pepper</strong></p><p>Put the tray[s] under the grill for 4-5 min or until the cheese has melted and the tomatoes have blistered – these are your <strong>pizza-style loaded beans on toast</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1695656388475-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1695656388475-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1695656388475-x700.jpg",
