            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>salad </strong>to a large bowl with the <strong>balsamic roasted cherry tomatoes</strong>, <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> and a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>– this is your <strong>balsamic tomato salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1695656393149-x200.jpg",
