            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>pizza-style loaded beans on toast</strong> with the <strong>balsamic tomato salad </strong>to the side</p><p>Garnish the beans with the <strong>remaining chopped basil</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
